thread.title: Heather Cosmo

author: Heather Cosmo
title: Heather Cosmo
text: We have been working with Five9 for over 1 year. We are very pleased with the online tool and the fact that our call centre employees can be spread out across the country but still be connected is so wonderful! In times when we have had to contact support we are always met with courtesy to resolve the problem at hand. We wouldn't hesitate to recommend this company and service to anyone looking for a solution to their call centre needs.
